    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exceptional vehicle, maintained in truly impeccable condition. This specimen exhibits no signs of wear, reflecting a standard of preservation that is rare in the pre-owned market. From its flawless exterior luster to the pristine, factory-fresh interior, every element remains in showroom state. Meticulously serviced and stored in a climate-controlled environment, this vehicle offers a peerless driving experience for the most discerning enthusiast. Opportunities to acquire a motorcar of this caliber are exceedingly rare.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
